        <type>__host__ void</type>
        <definition>__host__ void transferParams</definition>
        <argsstring>()</argsstring>
        <name>transferParams</name>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Synchronizes global host simulation parameters with device memory symbols. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Copies physics constants, grid dimensions, lookup tables and model-specific parameters from the host to the device using <computeroutput>cudaMemcpyToSymbol</computeroutput>.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="return"><para>void </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
        </inbodydescription>
