<para>Pointer to the <computeroutput><ref refid="structof__photonSOA" kindref="compound">of_photonSOA</ref></computeroutput> structure whose device members are to be freed. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
