        <briefdescription>
<para>Creates a 1D texture object from a 1D data array. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Converts input <computeroutput>double</computeroutput> data to <computeroutput>float</computeroutput>, uploads it to a 1D CUDA array, and initializes a texture object with linear filtering and clamp addressing.</para>
<para>This is used for the Modified Bessel function lookup table ( <formula id="43">$ K_2 $</formula>). <parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>texObj</parametername>
